The smallest-numbered unreserved seat should be able to be fetched by the system.The ability to reserve a seat should be present in the system.The reserved seat number should be able to be returned by the system.When all seats are available, the lowest numbered seat should be returned by the system.When there are multiple available seats, the lowest numbered seat should be returned by the system.When there are multiple available seats with the same number, the lowest numbered seat should be returned by the system.When there are multiple available seats with different numbers, the lowest numbered seat should be returned by the system.After reserving a seat, the list of available seats should be updated by the system.When there is only one seat left, the only available seat should be returned by the system.